social_posts.post_text: ‘Plant Lady’ | 12.2.22

‘The Still of Night’ | Limited edition print release with @curatecoffeeandart available now . Link in bio. Go check out @curatecoffeeandart if you interested in a great coffee subscription that comes with some cool art. I’m lucky to be the artist of the month for December. ❤️
@shiftcoffeebar making folks smile. @dawsonjordan flexin’ making me smile.
Recent art for bffs @mikemainsmusic
Anniversary T for @forevertattooparlour . Available for preorder now! Gettttt itttttt!
Album art for @rosscopperman Always honored to work on cover artwork. Especially when the music carry’s as much meaning and weight as Ross’s does. ❤️
Merrrrryyyyyyy Christmas!
Another great Christmas up north. ❤️
Just a bit late on this.. off to a really good start this year. Made a little 2023 calendar. Free download-print on your own calendar. Available now. Link in bio. Happy new year folks.
Helped out on the Mellow Mushroom staff Christmas gift. Mellow getting real mellow, won’t find this one in stores. INSIDERS ONLY.

“And it ain't the safest feeling
When the angel on your shoulder falls asleep.” Just for fun, inspired by some @rustonkelly lyrics.
Design for my bff Dave and his show at the Garden.
@colonyhouse about to take over the Mother Church tonight and kickoff there Cannonballers tour. Here’s the poster I designed for the special occasion. ❤️
Monday morning self portrait
Ro holding up my latest poster for DMB. This one was for there show in Phoenix this past weekend, at the Bud Light Super Bowl Music Fest. Just added it to shop if you like!

social_posts.post_text: Another one for the @colonyhouse boyz on tour now.

Every year @phish hosts an insane all-inclusive concert vacation featuring four nights of Phish performing on the beach in Cancun, Mexico. I was lucky enough to create one of the posters for the 2023 event. Had a lot of fun with this one. Thanks for @juliamordaunt for the opportunity. Both versions available on my site now.
Dang.. Cancun, Mexico sounds pretty good right about now. Dave and Tim got the right idea. Patch an pin designs for there recent shows in Riviera Maya.
This design is dedicated to todays weather. 🌞🌴

Set of posters for @theavettbrothers 2 night stay in St. Augustine this past Friday and Saturday. First time making a matching set and had a lot of fun with it. These two posters are available on my website now. ❤️

04.03.23 | steady & true.

Personal piece finished up on the way back home from Creative South. Fun hangs with new and old friends. Feeling inspired to get back to work. ❤️

‘Tropic like it’s hot’ | My contribution to @bandits_bandanas new Tropical collection. Funnnnn stufff. Also! Inspired by their relief efforts in and around Ft. Myers, a portion of the proceeds from my bandana will go to @americanredcross . Link in bio to snag one!
Made a couple of very unofficial @taylorswift T’s for a very official @taylorswift concert with @annie_noom ❤️

Big W last night @cavs . Gotta take that energy to to MSG. 🏀🔥 

Side note, I’ve been enjoying incorporating some photos into my designs. Something fun about mixing illustration and photography.
3 cups of coffee by 10am kind of morning.
Super choppy new display ‘font’ added to the shop. Go on and get it before I realize how bad it is and take it down. ❤️
…Something. | 05.16.23
Haveafunfriday.jpeg
New one for my bffs @shiftcoffeebar
Poster design for my best friend Dave’s show last night in Wilmington, NC. Available now in my shop if you like!
Had the opportunity to work on a couple pieces for @noahkahanmusic . Stoked on this one. That’s for the shot @mikey_lavi

New one for @bandanaofthemonthclub . I’m stoked to be the featured artist for June. I’ve seen so many folks put out really cool bandanas with BOTMC that I was excited to have a go myself. Available now until June 30.

Stoked on this poster design for @mymorningjacket show last night in St. Augustine. Also stoked it was a Florida show. Also stoked that @wilderado_ was the special guest. Fun one! As always @vahalla killed it on the print job. Poster up for grabs on my site now!
Anniversary T for @palacepubandwine  Congrats on 4 years!!! This town wouldn’t be the same without ya! @graveyardshiftscreenprinting killing it as always.
“ 🖐️ I’m a whole hand now” - Ro. Happy 5th Rowan! 💜 🎉
Illustration for @johnmarkmcmillan acoustic tour. These are going to be special nights… there’s no doubt. Check his page for more details.
A few days into our trip and The Dolomites do not disappoint. 🇮🇹
Drawn somewhere up in the sky in between Venice and Montreal on the way home from Italy.
A little slow to share this one but I finally added these posters to the shop. Another fun one for Mr. Dave Matthew’s. This time live and acoustic from NYC. ❤️

Phish live at the Garden! You can find the art on T’s and hats, but what’s most cool are these banners made by @oxfordpennant . So stoked about these. Thanks @phish and @juliamordaunt for another fun project!
@mymorningjacket - Washington, DC - I had a lot of fun with the concept and I’m really pleased with how it came out. @vahalla crushed the print job as always. Available now in my shop!
null
Illustration for @phish latest run in PA. 🔨 🍌

My Morning Jacket + Fleet foxes! In LA!  Was very very stoked to work on this one. Available now in the shop. Even got a few fancy foil variants up for grabs too. The team at @vahalla absolutely smashed the printing on this one.❤️
Probably should be working but I’m playing with my daughters clay instead.

First of a few designs for @nashvillesc rolled out yesterday. First up, Jacob Shaffelburg, the ’Tennessee Waterslide’. It was a real privilege to work with @nickbastoky and the creative team over at NSC. Looking forward to the rest dropping soon.
Hanging out at @springfieldcreatives this Wednesday. If you’re in/around that area come and hang! We’ll be talking about client feedback and all that ‘fun stuff’. ❤️
Latest poster design for @theavettbrothers . Always so fun. They told me the venue was at a winery and that led me here. Available now in the shop. ❤️

Poster design for @mumfordandsons . Was very excited about this opportunity. Been a fan of M&S for a looooong time. Also, love the fact that it’s a FL show and I got to lean into that a little bit. My friends at @native_screenprintco crushed the print job! Available in shop now!
A little summer something for @davematthewsband
It’s my 35th birthday today. I had gummy bears and donuts for breakfast so I’m feeling wild. 35% off all posters on my site. Use code ‘HAPPYBDAY’ for discount. ❤️
Anniversary’s T for @kapownoodlebar . Congrats on 12 years!
getting kinda bad at drawing but its kinda fun
Back at it for @theory11 . This time for Rick and Morty… I tried my best to cram as much R&M imagery and nuggets from the show into these as possible. Hope you like! Wubba-lubba-dub-dub!
Inspired by last week’s gravel ride.
Latest design for @noahkahanmusic just dropped alongside a bunch of other cool stuff. Been great working. with @mikey_lavi on these designs, thanks dude!
12.19.23 | Been a minute but still making stuff.
Merry Christmas ❤️
And around we go again… Happy new year folks. ❤️
